Description: Fits supervised topic models to count data (e.g. gene expression)
    jointly with a binary or categorical response via integrated non-negative
    matrix factorization and latent Dirichlet allocation, using Stan (via
    cmdstanr) for full Bayesian inference and an EM warm-start for
    initialization. Provides cross-validation, prediction on new samples, and
    diagnostic plots for topic-response associations.
